Docs.summary: A convention that finds entity types which share a table which has a concurrency token column where those entity types do not have a property mapped to that column. It then creates a shadow concurrency property mapped to that column on the base-most entity type(s).
Docs.remarks: See Model building conventions for more information and examples.
